      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that but i dont want to bother my doctor for every little thing. like, if im feeling totally fine and my heart isnt acting up, isnt it a sign that the 5mg is actually more than i need? people always say less is more when u feel healthy. wouldn't a smaller dose like 2mg be a safer way to just maintain where i'm at without overdoing the chemicals?",
